fields.name: saltymoose
fields.description:
Our Salty Moose range uses salt-base nicotine to provide a quicker nicotine hit on the draw, mimicking the effect of those cigarettes you're glad you quit. Available in our hassle-free 10ml bottles, choose either 10mg or 20mg nicotine concentration depending on your needs.

Our flavours have been blended to provide the smoothest, tastiest vape.

If you're using a mouth-to-lung device, Salty Moose is the perfect compliment.
